{"text": " Make a long exhale from the nose, from the chest, from the belly. Inhale freely, easily onto your empty body. Exhale in a vertical from the top, from the chest. Pull the belly inwards to push out the air from your body. And now use your exhale to bring your mind lower to the abdominal area. Lower abdomen towards the belly. With each exhalation, bring your attention lower towards the center of gravity. From thinking to centering in the point of gravity. Use your exhale to bring yourself lower to the belly. From thought to the center, to the center. Back to center. Attention on the center of gravity. Deep in the belly. When thoughts arise, exhale from the chest, from the belly, connect through the center of gravity. Exhale in the center. Inhale in the center.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 0.0, "end": 11.84, "text": " Make a long exhale from the nose, from the chest, from the belly.", "tokens": [50364, 4387, 257, 938, 19652, 490, 264, 6690, 11, 490, 264, 7443, 11, 490, 264, 11696, 13, 51064], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.27909790674845375, "compression_ratio": 1.2674418604651163, "no_speech_prob": 0.04331669956445694, "words": [{"word": " Make", "start": 0.0, "end": 2.44, "probability": 0.737825334072113}, {"word": " a", "start": 2.44, "end": 2.68, "probability": 0.9407491087913513}, {"word": " long", "start": 2.68, "end": 3.26, "probability": 0.9900930523872375}, {"word": " exhale", "start": 3.26, "end": 4.14, "probability": 0.9945148229598999}, {"word": " from", "start": 4.14, "end": 5.36, "probability": 0.9283446073532104}, {"word": " the", "start": 5.36, "end": 5.58, "probability": 0.9958003163337708}, {"word": " nose,", "start": 5.58, "end": 6.04, "probability": 0.995947539806366}, {"word": " from", "start": 6.68, "end": 8.26, "probability": 0.9877175092697144}, {"word": " the", "start": 8.26, "end": 8.48, "probability": 0.9961864352226257}, {"word": " chest,", "start": 8.48, "end": 9.0, "probability": 0.9991545677185059}, {"word